eferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16522386%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F16522386%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENews%20agency%20ANI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1748721862174232755%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20an%20unnamed%20official%20from%20AIIMS%20to%20say%20that%20those%20who%20miss%20their%20OPDs%20on%20Monday%2C%20January%2022%2C%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98accommodated%20if%20they%20come%E2%80%99.%20The%20ANI%20also%20said%20that%20the%20evening%20OPDs%20would%20be%20running%20as%20usual%20at%20AIIMS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20evening%20OPDs%20are%20different%20from%20morning%E2%80%99s%20and%20are%20offered%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eonly%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Efor%20some%20select%20services.%20It%20is%20not%20clear%20yet%2C%20as%20to%20how%2C%20the%2013%2C000%20patients%2C%20who%20had%20their%20scheduled%20appointments%20on%20Monday%20can%20be%20%E2%80%98accommodated%E2%80%99%20over%20and%20above%20the%20routine%20OPD%20services%20on%20any%20given%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20official%20word%20from%20AIIMS%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98No%20civilised%20country%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20cruel%20%5Bfor%20patients%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20AIIMS%20professor%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20as%20the%20person%20was%20not%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20no%20civilised%20country%20this%20can%20be%20allowed%20to%20happen.%20We%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20anything%20like%20this%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20professor%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20professor%20explained%20on%20gazetted%20holidays%20and%20weekends%20these%20services%20are%20not%20scheduled%20itself%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20so%20patients%20don%E2%80%99t%20suffer%20sudden%20and%20mass%20cancellations%20like%20it%20has%20happened%20this%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20hospitals%20like%20AIIMS%2C%20people%2C%20who%20come%20from%20far%20flung%20areas%20of%20the%20country%20and%20neighbouring%20ones%20queue%20up%20from%20early%20in%20the%20morning%20for%20registration%2C%20and%20often%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20months%20to%20finally%20get%20an%20appointment%20to%20see%20a%20doctor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20IMA%20president%20Sharad%20Aggarwal%20for%20comments%20on%20this%20unprecedented%20development%20of%20sorts.%20He%20did%20not%20give%20a%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20hospital%20notification%20said%20all%20services%20will%20remain%20closed%20till%202.30%20pm%20but%20OPD%20registrations%20would%20start%20at%201.30%20pm.%20But%20for%20how%20long%20would%20it%20continue%20and%20how%20many%20appointments%20would%20be%20given%20was%20not%C2%A0%20clear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Vardhman%20Mahavir%20Medical%20College%20associated%20with%20Safdarjung%20hospital%20issued%20a%20clarification%20to%20its%20earlier%20notification%20saying%20OPD%20registration%20will%20happen%20from%208%20am%20to%2010%20am%2C%20instead%20of%20what%20would%20usually%20be%208.30%20am%20to%2011.30%20am.%20A%20similar%20note%20was%20put%20out%20by%20Lady%20Hardinge%20hospital%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurgeries%20to%20take%20a%20hit%20as%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20all%20the%20notifications%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20planned%20surgeries%20for%20Monday%20would%20not%20be%20conducted.%20A%20back-of-the-envelope%20calculation%20suggests%20that%20an%20estimated%201%2C200%20surgeries%20would%20be%20delayed%20in%20three%20major%20hospitals%20of%20Delhi%20that%20are%20run%20by%20the%20central%20government%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20AIIMS%2C%20Safdarjung%20hospital%20and%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20Hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16522399%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16522399%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F16522399%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20all%20the%20three%20hospitals%2C%20the%20biggest%20hit%20would%20of%20course%20be%20taken%20by%20AIIMS%2C%20which%20conducts%20close%20to%20800%20surgeries%20per%20day%2C%20as%20the%20data%20above%20shows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20these%20surgeries%20are%20minor%20while%20others%20are%20major%20and%20complicated%20ones.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fdelhi%2Fwant-a-surgery-at-aiims-wait-could-be-four-years%2Fstory-Ndl1iIL8wFEn4Vm5fNPoBM.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Esuggest%20the%20wait%20time%20for%20these%20surgeries%20can%20range%20from%20as%20many%20as%20two%20to%20four%20years.%20Patients%20dying%2C%20while%20they%20are%20kept%20waiting%20by%20these%20hospitals%20for%20surgeries%20due%20to%20overcrowding%2C%20is%20no%20secret.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20now%20as%20to%20when%20these%20surgeries%2C%20which%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20done%20on%20Monday%2C%20would%20find%20a%20date%20and%20time%20again%20and%20how%20soon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20just%20surgeries%20and%20OPD%20appointments%2C%20even%20lab%20investigations%20are%20going%20to%20suffer.%20Except%20for%20Safdarjung%20hospital%2C%20which%20said%20lab%20and%20radiological%20services%20would%20be%20available%20till%20the%20truncated%20time%20of%2011.30%20am%2C%20none%20of%20the%20other%20three%20hospitals%20%E2%80%93%20AIIMS%2C%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20hospital%20and%20Lady%20Hardinge%20College%20Hospital%20said%20anything%20of%20this%20sort.%20A%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fwait-for-mri-at-aiims-delhi-still-up-to-one-year-despite-24x7-tests-101688496232044.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Equoted%20doctors%20of%20radiology%20department%20as%20saying%20wait%20for%20MRI%2C%20a%20radiological%20service%2C%20can%20be%20upto%201%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705804508000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21080329%2FUntitled-design-17.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhospitals-january-22-ram-temple-holiday-surgeries-opd%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20did%20a%20back-of-the-envelope%20calculation%2C%20assuming%20the%20hospitals%20offer%20these%20services%20at%20least%20in%20320%20days%20a%20year%2C%20minus%20weekends%20and%20gazetted%20holidays.%20These%20estimates%20suggest%20that%20more%20than%2032%2C000%20people%20would%20stand%20to%20suffer%20as%20hospitals%20have%20been%20ordered%20shut%20till%202.30%20pm%20on%20January%2022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22cano