Fenglish.adhadhu.com%2Farticle%2F48634%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20began%20to%20unfold%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20when%20the%20child%20suffered%20a%20stroke%2C%20prompting%20his%20family%20to%20request%20an%20aerial%20transfer%20to%20the%20capital.%20However%2C%20their%20distress%20calls%20went%20unanswered%20until%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20when%20the%20country's%20aviation%20authorities%20finally%20responded.%20The%20delay%2C%20reportedly%20lasting%2016%20crucial%20hours%2C%20sparked%20protests%20near%20the%20hospital%20in%20Gaaf%20Alif%20Villingili%20as%20the%20community%20voiced%20their%20anger%20over%20the%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grief-stricken%20father%2C%20speaking%20to%20local%20media%20outlet%20Adhahu%2C%20lamented%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20prompt%20response%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20called%20Island%20Aviation%20to%20get%20him%20to%20Male%20immediately%20after%20the%20stroke%20but%20they%20did%20not%20answer%20our%20calls.%20They%20answered%20the%20phone%20at%208%3A30%20am%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20solution%20is%20to%20have%20an%20air%20ambulance%20for%20such%20cases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20subsequent%20transfer%20to%20Male%2C%20although%20accomplished%2C%20was%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20child's%20rapidly%20deteriorating%20health.%20Upon%20arrival%2C%20the%20boy%20was%20immediately%20admitted%20to%20an%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit%20(ICU).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAasandha%20Company%20Limited%2C%20the%20company%20responsible%20for%20medical%20evacuations%2C%20issued%20a%20statement%20indicating%20that%20they%20had%20initiated%20the%20evacuation%20process%20promptly%20upon%20receiving%20the%20request.%20However%2C%20they%20cited%20a%20last-minute%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20glitch%26quot%3B%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20with%20deep%20regret%20that%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20unfortunate%20passing%20of%20the%20patient%20involved%20in%20the%20emergency%