ould-bar-universal-basic-income-programs-in-iowa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Gazette%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Cedar%20Rapids-based%20newspaper.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legis.iowa.gov%2Flegislation%2FBillBook%3Fga%3D90%26ba%3DHSB552%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebill%3C%2Fa%3E%20threatens%20those%20who%20don't%20comply%20with%20prosecution%20by%20the%20state%20attorney%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20tell%20you%20right%20now%3A%20This%20is%20socialism%20on%20steroids.%20This%20is%20a%20redistribution%20of%20wealth.%20This%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20American%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Holt%20said%20in%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWheeler%20added%20that%20he%20thinks%20such%20programs%20are%20%26quot%3Binsane%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20more%20reliance%20on%20government%26quot%3B%20by%20taking%20money%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20hardworking%20taxpayers%20and%20giving%20it%20to%20those%20that%20are%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHolt%20called%20basic%20income%20programs%20an%20%26quot%3Battack%20on%20the%20work%20ethic%20in%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%20Both%20state%20reps%20said%20that%20the%20initiatives%20incentivize%20people%20not%20to%20seek%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20cities%20that%20have%20implemented%20such%20programs%2C%20however%2C%20have%20seen%20success.%20The%20Baltimore%20Young%20Families%20Success%20Fund%20gives%20young%20mothers%20up%20to%20%241%2C000%20monthly%2C%20no%20strings%20attached.%20The%20deal%20is%20so%20good%20some%20applicants%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20scam.%20The%20campaign's%20director%20of%20policy%2C%20Tonaeya%20Moore%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguaranteed-universal-basic-income-ubi-baltimore-young-families-success-fund-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20surveys%20show%20that%20participants%20largely%20spent%20their%20money%20on%20the%20same%20general%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20bills%2C%20car%20%5Bpayments%5D%2C%20groceries%2C%20childcare%2C%26quot%3B%20Moore%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20our%20families%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20them%2C%20even%20after%20the%20thousand%20dollars%2C%20they%20still%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20help%2C%20so%20no%20one's%20taking%20advantage%2C%26quot%3B%20Moore%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguaranteed-income-program-flint-michigan-new-moms-500-a-month-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguaranteed%20basic%20income%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20launched%20in%20Flint%2C%20Michigan%2C%20offers%20mothers%20a%20lump%20sum%20payment%20of%20%241%2C500%20during%20pregnancy%20and%20another%20%24500%20each%20month%20during%20their%20baby's%20first%20year%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%20The%20program%2C%20called%20RxKids%2C%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20now-defunct%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchild-poverty-rate-america-congress-cut-biden-expanded-tax-credit-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EChild%20Tax%20Credit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20pandemic-era%20relief%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENalo%20Johnson%2C%20president%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20Mid-Iowa%20Health%20Foundation%2C%20spoke%20at%20the%20hearing%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Gazette.%20The%20foundation's%20project%2C%20%26quot%3BUpLift%2C%26quot%3B%20provides%20110%20low-income%20central%20Iowans%20with%20%24500%20a%20month%20for%20two%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UpLift%20project%20receives%20funding%20from%20public%2C%20private%2C%20charity%2C%20and%20nonprofit%20sources%2C%20The%20Gazette%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20the%20foundation%20is%20primarily%20interested%20in%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20basic%20income%20is%20shown%20not%20