to%20capacity.%20Slots%20at%20Varanasi%2C%20a%20city%20around%20four%20hours%20away%20by%20car%2C%20are%20also%20full%2C%20as%20are%20jet%20spaces%20in%20Gorakhpur%20airport%2C%20which%20is%20a%20three-hour%20drive%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehra%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20price%20of%20the%20charters%2C%20but%20private%20jet%20booking%20website%20JetSetGo%20lists%20the%20price%20of%20a%20Mumbai-Gorakhpur%20flight%20on%20a%20Falcon%202000%20jet%20with%20nine%20passengers%20on%20board%20at%20about%20%2474%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20is%20also%20giving%20jewellers%20and%20gold%20traders%20a%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20retailers%20say%20gold%20and%20gold-plated%20statues%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20temple%20replicas%20-%20priced%20at%20between%20Rs%2030%2C000%20(%24361)%20and%20Rs%20220%2C000%20(%242%2C647)%20-%20are%20so%20popular%20that%20they%20have%20run%20out%20of%20stock.%20Some%20items%20were%20imported%20from%20Thailand%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20are%20asking%20for%20them%20for%20gifting%20and%20for%20keeping%20them%20at%20homes.%20There%20is%20a%20waiting%20period%20of%20two%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Baldev%20Singh%2C%20a%20manager%20at%20HS%20Jewellers%20in%20Lucknow%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20has%20already%20ushered%20an%20economic%20boom%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20set%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20pilgrimage%20hotspot%20for%20India's%201.1%20billion%20Hindus%2C%20and%20property%20prices%20have%20skyrocketed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Bollywood%20superstar%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20bought%20a%2010%2C000%20square%20foot%20(929%20square%20meter)%20plot%20for%20%241.7%20million%2C%20government%20officials%20said%2C%20roughly%20nine%20times%20the%20average%20land%20prices%20in%20this%20dusty%20city%20just%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%20is%20part%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Abhinandan%20Lodha%20(HoABL)%20luxury%20development%20which%20includes%20a%20spa%20and%20a%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20huge%20demand%20for%20the%20project%20from%20domestic%20professionals%2C%20non-resident%20Indians.%20This%20is%20unlike%20any%20other%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20HoABL%20Chairman%20Abhinandan%20Lodha%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20betting%20on%20economic%20prosperity%20but%20there's%20also%20emotional%20attachment%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705776720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F39fpoaa8_gold-plated-idols_120x90_21_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-inauguration-devotees-splurge-on-jets-gold-plated-idols-as-ram-temple-opens-monday-4901139%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20private%20jet%20parking%20lots%20at%20airports%20near%20the%20city%20of%20Ayodhya%20are%20full%20and%20the%20shops%20have%20run%20out%20of%20gold-plated%20idols%2C%20as%20wealthy%20devotees%20prepare%20for%20the%20invite-only%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20one%20of%20Hinduism's%20holiest%20temples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-inauguration-devotees-splurge-on-jets-gold-plated-idols-as-ram-temple-opens-monday-4901139%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-inauguration-devotees-splurge-on-jets-gold-plated-idols-as-ram-temple-opens-monday-4901139%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fayodhya-ram-temple-inauguration-devotees-splurge-on-jets-gold-plated-idols-as-ram-temple-opens-monday-4901139%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Griselda%20Blanco's%20family%20says%20Netflix%20acted%20like%20her%20son%2C%20Michael%20Blanco%2C%20'did%20not%20exist'%20after%20he%20shared%20his%20mother's%20story%20with%20the%20streamer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%