2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20officially%20called%20the%20'Surya%20Tilak%20mechanism'.%20It%20was%20a%20scientific%20and%20engineering%20challenge%20to%20get%20it%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Surya%20Tilak%20mechanism%20would%20be%20fully%20operational%20when%20the%20full%20temple%20is%20constructed%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Ramancharla%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20Central%20Building%20Research%20Institute%20(CBRI)%2C%20Roorkee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBRI%20is%20India's%20top%20institution%2C%20which%20is%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20(CSIR).%20Currently%2C%20only%20the%20structure%20till%20the%20first%20floor%20has%20been%20made%2C%20says%20Dr%20Ramancharla.%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20equipment%20that%20was%20to%20be%20installed%20in%20the%20garba%20griha%20and%20ground%20floor%20has%20been%20completed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Surya%20Tilak%20mechanism%20is%20designed%20by%20a%20team%20of%20scientists%20from%20the%20CBRI%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20sunrays%20will%20fall%20on%20the%20forehead%20of%20Lord%20Ram's%20idol%20at%2012%20pm%20on%20Ram%20Navami%20day%20every%20year%20for%20about%20six%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20gearbox%20and%20reflective%20mirrors%20and%20lenses%20have%20been%20arranged%20such%20that%20sunrays%20from%20the%20third%20floor%20near%20the%20shikara%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20Garbha%20Griha%20using%20well-known%20principles%20of%20tracking%20the%20Sun's%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkqbluumg_surya-tilak_625x300_20_January_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIA)%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20provided%20technical%20support%20on%20the%20Sun's%20path%20and%20Optica%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20company%2C%20is%20involved%20in%20manufacturing%20the%20lenses%20and%20brass%20tubes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fabrication%20and%20installation%20of%20this%20device%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20Rajendra%20Kotaria%2C%20MD%20of%20Optica.%20The%20team%20from%20CBRI%20was%20led%20by%20Dr%20SK%20Panigrahi%2C%20along%20with%20Dr%20RS%20Bisht%2C%20Kanti%20Lal%20Solanki%2C%20V%20Chakradhar%2C%20Dinesh%2C%20and%20Sameer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBRI%20scientist%20Dr%20Pradeep%20Chauhan%2C%20who%20helped%20in%20the%20design%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B100%20per%20cent%20the%20Surya%20Tilak%20will%20anoint%20the%20forehead%20of%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20date%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20is%20fixed%20using%20the%20lunar%20calendar%2C%20special%20arrangements%20of%2019%20gears%20had%20to%20be%20put%20in%20place%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20auspicious%20anointment%20takes%20place%20as%20scheduled.%20%26quot%3BNo%20electricity%20or%20battery%20or%20iron%20is%20used%20in%20the%20gear-based%20Surya%20Tilak%20mechanism%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Chauhan%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20foremost%20institution%20on%20all%20issues%20astronomy%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20(IIA)%20came%20up%20with%20the%20solution%20to%20bridge%20the%20seemingly%20intractable%20confluence%20of%20the%20lunar%20and%20solar%20(Gregorian)%20calendars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20necessary%20expertise%20on%20positional%20astronomy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Annapurni%20Subramaniam%2C%20director%20of%20IIA.%20%26quot%3BThis%20domain%20knowledge%20was%20translated%20so%20that%20the%20Sun's%20rays%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20surya%20tilak%20could%20then%20anoint%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20every%20Ram%20Navami.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fv2epqa88_surya-tilak_625x300_20_January_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IIA%20also%20had%20the%20expertise%20with%20optics%20as%20they%20have%20designed%20some%20of%20India's%20best%20telescopes.%20That%20was%20extended%20to%20make%20sure%20this%20periscope-like%20device%20brings%20sunlight%20into%20the%20enclosed%20garba%20griha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20interesting%20scientific%20experiment%20where%20the%2019-year%20repeat%20cycle%20of%20the%20two%20calendars'%20helped%20solve%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Subramaniam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Sun's%20energy%20will%20be%20harvested%20and%20directed%20to%20the%20forehead%20of%20the%20idol%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20another%20equally%20ambitious%20project%20to%20make%20the%20Ram%20temple%20complex%20green%20and%20near%20net-zero%20by%20using%20solar%20energy%20panels%20to%20generate%20electricity%20could%20not%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20presence%20of%20many%20monkey%20troops%20led%20to%20the%20abandoning%20of%20the%20solar%20energy%20project%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Nripendra%20Misra%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20temple%20construction%20committee%20of%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20so%20many%20monkeys%2C%20and%20they%20are%20all%20revered.%20They%20would%20have%20damaged%20the%20exposed%20solar%20panels%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20surya%20tilak%20mechanism%20already%20exists%20in%20some%20Jain%20temples%20and%20at%20the%20Sun%20Temple%20at%20Konark%2C%20but%20they%20are%20engineered%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705776240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fms9tme7_surya-tilak_625x