nk%5C%22%3Eforce%20Israel%20to%20adhere%20to%20international%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20continue%20receiving%20American%20military%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20amendment%20from%20Sen.%20Tim%20Kaine%20of%20Virginia%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kaine.senate.gov%2Fpress-releases%2Fkaine-to-file-amendment-to-maintain-congressional-oversight-of-foreign-military-assistance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewould%20prevent%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20transferring%20weapons%20to%20Israel%20without%20congressional%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20a%20bill%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsanders-urges-biden-revoke-financial-support-israel-netanyahu-gaza-palestinians-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESen.%20Bernie%20Sanders%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Vermont%2C%20who%20received%20flack%20from%20his%20progressive%20supporters%20early%20on%20for%20his%20full-throated%20support%20of%20Israel%2C%20would%20have%20forced%20Biden%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fsenate-rejects-bernie-sanders-bid-probe-israel-gaza-human-rights-concerns%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestigate%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20abuses%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESanders'%20bill%20was%20rejected%20this%20week.%20And%20even%20though%20so%20far%20only%20a%20small%20(but%20growing)%20number%20of%20mainstream%20Democrats%20have%20signed%20on%20to%20some%20of%20these%20other%20measures%2C%20their%20very%20existence%20is%20significant%20and%20a%20sign%20of%20a%20political%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESupport%20for%20Israel%20has%20forever%20been%20one%20of%20the%20few%20bipartisan%20certainties%20in%20Washington.%20But%20the%20scale%20of%20destruction%20and%20death%20in%20Gaza%20has%20led%20to%20a%20groundswell%20of%20worldwide%20sympathy%20for%20Palestinians%20and%20a%20decrease%20in%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20changing%20political%20calculations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20poll%20released%20last%20