height%3D%5C%224302%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGov.%20Wes%20Moore%20of%20Maryland%2C%20center%2C%20and%20Rep.%20Steny%20Hoyer%20share%20the%20stage%20in%20Baltimore.%3Cp%3EBill%20Clark%2FCQ-Roll%20Call%2C%20Inc%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20GSA%20announced%20that%20Maryland%20had%20been%20picked%20to%20land%20the%20new%20FBI%20headquarters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMaryland%20lawmakers%2C%20including%20Gov.%20Wes%20Moore%20and%20Rep.%20Steny%20Hoyer%2C%C2%A0emphasized%20equity%20in%20their%20pitch.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20Virginia%20officials%20who%20have%20decried%20the%20selection%20process%20now%20want%20it%20reversed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20a%20bipartisan%20contingent%20of%20political%20leaders%20in%20Maryland%20and%20Virginia%20sought%20to%20land%20the%20new%20FBI%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20J.%20Edgar%20Hoover%20Building%2C%20a%20Brutalist%20complex%20near%20the%20White%20House%20that%20has%20housed%20the%20agency's%20headquarters%20since%201975%2C%20became%20functionally%20obsolete%20years%20ago%2C%20with%20employees%20dispersed%20among%20different%20locations%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20current%20location%2C%20while%20centrally%20located%2C%20also%20has%20security%20vulnerabilities%20that%20a%20newer%20and%20more%20secure%20facility%20would%20rectify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20race%20to%20land%20the%20facility%20was%20intense.%20But%20federal%20officials%20last%20November%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gsa.gov%2Fabout-us%2Fgsa-regions%2Fregion-11-national-capital%2Fbuildings-and-facilities%2Fdevelopment-projects%2Ffbi-hq-consolidation%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520agency%2520determined%2520that%2520Greenbelt%2Csite%2520for%2520the%2520FBI%2520HQ.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselected%20a%20site%20in%20Greenbelt%2C%20Maryland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20located%20in%20suburban%20Prince%20George's%20County%20and%20adjacent%20to%20an%20existing%20Metro%20station%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20easily%20accessible%20to%20public%20transit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgovernor.maryland.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress%2Fpages%2Fgovernor-moore-and-team-maryland-welcome-the-selection-of-greenbelt-for-new-fbi-headquarters.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20major%20win%20for%20Maryland%20Gov.%20Wes%20Moore%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Maryland%20Sens.%20Ben%20Cardin%20and%20Chris%20Van%20Hollen%2C%20but%20especially%20for%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Steny%20Hoyer%2C%20the%20dean%20of%20the%20Maryland%20congressional%20delegation%20and%20a%20longtime%20champion%20of%20the%20project.%20Hoyer%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20told%20me%20that%20he%20first%20discussed%20the%20move%20in%202009%20with%20then-FBI%20director%20Robert%20Mueller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20down%20to%20the%20building%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20it%2C%20took%20a%20tour%20through%20it%2C%20and%20he%20showed%20me%20how%20decrepit%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoyer%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20Mueller%20said%20the%20state%20of%20the%20building%20was%20undermining%20the%20agency's%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoyer%2C%20a%20former%20House%20majority%20leader%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marylandmatters.org%2F2022%2F04%2F29%2Fpolitical-notes-hoyer-endorses-wes-moore-for-governor-plus-legislative-candidates-backed-by-casa-in-action-sierra-club%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Moore's%20campaign%20months%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaryland-governor-house-primary-elections-live-results-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20Democratic%20gubernatorial%20primary%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20now-governor%20%26quot%3Bimmediately%20seized%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20FBI%20issue%20even%20before%20his%20eventual%20win%20in%20the%20primary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20digested%20and%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20our%20competitive%20advantage%20and%20focused%20on%20achieving%20that%20objective%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoyer%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20he%20recognized%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20FBI%20for%20Maryland%20and%20in%20particular%20for%20Prince%20George's%20County.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrince%20George's%20County%2C%20the%20majority-Black%20county%20directly%20to%20the%20east%20of%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20has%20for%20years%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2022%2F06%2F29%2Fdept-of-data-prince-georges-richest-black-county%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20most%20affluent%20Black%20populations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20any%20jurisdiction%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20compared%20to%20Northern%20Virginia%20localities%20like%20Fairfax%20County%2C%20which%20has%20been%20an%20economic%20powerhouse%20for%20decades%2C%20Prince%20George's%20County%20hasn't%20enjoyed%20a%20similar%20level%20of%20economic%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FBI%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65abfc99dcdb354a98596d66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20J.%20Edgar%20Hoover%20Building%20in%20downtown%20Washington%20is%20an%20outdated%20facility%20that%20doesn't%20serve%20the%20FBI's%20long-term%20needs.%3Cp%3EERIC%20BARADAT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20sense%2C%20the%20new%20building%20%E2%80%94%20which%20will%20consolidate%20and%20hold%20roughly%2011%2C000%20employees%20under%20one%20roof%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%204%25%20of%20leased%20federal%20office%20space%20in%20Prince%20George's%20County%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoyer%20told%20me%2C%20while%20also%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20county%20is%20home%20to%20roughly%2020%25%20of%20the%20Washington%20region's%20federal%20workers.%20%26quot%3BFairfax%20County%20has%2011%25%20of%20the%20office%20space%2C%20almost%20three%20times%20as%20much%20as%20we%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoyer%2C%20like%20Moore%2C%20argued%20during%20the%20selection%20process%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2023%2F03%2F08%2Ffbi-headquarters-wes-moore-maryland%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Maryland%20site%20would%20be%20tied%20to%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20race%20but%20also%20regarding%20the%20level%20of%20federal%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20project%20will%20be%20worth%20over%20%244%20billion%20in%20economic%20activity%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20solidify%20Maryland%20as%20the%20cyber%20capital%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20governor%20told%20me%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20that%20we%20made%20it%20such%20a%20high%20priority%20is%20because%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20federal%20buildings%20that%20has%20ever%20been%20built.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVirginia%20leaders%2C%20who%20for%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fdc-md-va%2F2023%2F06%2F08%2Ffbi-headquarters-maryland-virginia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20suburban%20site%20near%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20Base%20Quantico%20was%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20the%20headquarters%2C%20have%20criticized%20the%20selection%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20the%20General%20Service%20Administration%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffbi-headquarters-investigation-virginia-maryland-9c923cd2909eb3597708d498c859f44b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econduct%20an%20evaluation%20of%20the%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbeyer.house.gov%2Fnews%2Fdocumentsingle.aspx%3FDocumentID%3D6028%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20November%20letter%3C%