3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Reserve%20hiked%20rates%2011%20times%20in%20the%202022-2023%20cycle%2C%20spiking%20its%20benchmark%20rate%20from%20near%200%25%20to%20a%20range%20of%205.25%25-5.50%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20I've%20kind%20of%20revised%20my%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20circumstances%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20likely%20we%20do%20see%20much%20slower%20growth%20in%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20inverted%20yield%20curve%2C%20in%20one%20sense%2C%20is%20a%20self-fulfilling%20prophecy%20as%20it%20signals%20to%20companies%20and%20investors%20that%20a%20slowdown%20is%20looming%2C%20which%20then%20alters%20spending%20and%20business%20behavior%20and%20ultimately%20leads%20to%20less%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20the%20yield%20curve%20causal%2C%26quot%3B%20Harvey%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20causality%20channel%20is%20much%20different%20than%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20inversion%20itself%20also%20isn't%20the%20final%20call%20on%20a%20recession%2C%20as%20experts%20have%20noted%20that%20it%20is%20actually%20when%20the%20curve%20de-inverts%20and%20long-term%20yields%20again%20exceed%20those%20of%20short-term%20bonds%20that%20signals%20a%20downturn%20has%20arrived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20its%20perfect%20track%20record%2C%20Harvey%20noted%20that%20the%20indicator%20is%20currently%20allowing%20firms%20to%20make%20smarter%20decisions%20in%20the%20current%20landscape%20and%20operate%20with%20more%20caution.%20Unlike%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%20in%202008%2C%20he%20said%20companies%20are%20more%20strategic%20and%20managing%20risk%2C%20so%20he's%20hopeful%20that%20there%20won't%20be%20severe%20layoffs%20coming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndeed%20it%20could%20come%20to%20the%20point%20where%20the%20indicator%20could%20come%20to%20the%20point%20where%20the%20indicator%20just%20loses%20its%20ability%20to%20forecast%2C%26quot%3B%