%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fbehindthescenes-glimpse-michael-jacksons-biopic-unveils-first-look%2Farticleshow%2F107014982.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Of%20Narcissism%20and%20Submissive%20Masochism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20a%20senior%20journalist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmkvenu1%2Fstatus%2F1745290792795517395%3Fs%3D46%26t%3D1vwSP919utJCl83SiqVxmg%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter)%20an%20officially%20sponsored%20visual%20image%20relating%20to%20the%20January%2022%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20that%20portrays%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20holy%20robes%20and%20respectfully%20folded%20hands%2C%20towering%20over%20a%20miniscule%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla.%20This%20was%20his%20accompanying%20caption%3A%20%E2%80%9CNarcissism%20is%20often%20embedded%20in%20the%20visual%20image.%20See%20the%20sheer%20contrast%20between%20the%20stature%20of%20man%20and%20God!%20The%20devotee%20seems%20the%20medium%20as%20well%20as%20the%20message.%E2%80%9D%20It%20set%20me%20thinking!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20month%2C%20the%20media%20has%20inundated%20us%20with%20such%20posters%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20anointed%20man%20eclipsing%20God%20(one%20poster%20shows%20our%20Supreme%20Leader%20holding%20the%20toddler%20Ram%20Lalla%20by%20his%20finger%20and%20escorting%20him%20to%20the%20temple)%20which%20makes%20one%20cudgel%20the%20brains%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20who%20the%20star%20is%20and%20who%20the%20supporting%20cast%20in%20this%20glitzy%20celebration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20leaving%20alone%20the%20Almighty%20from%20this%20blasphemous%20false%20equivalence%2C%20we%20know%20who%20the%20chosen%20one%20is%20in%20our%20benighted%20country%20because%20we%20have%20his%20word%20for%20it.%20In%20a%20special%20audio%20message%20released%20on%20January%2012%2C%20announcing%20a%20special%20ritual%20ahead%20of%20the%20grand%20event%20%E2%80%93%20a%2011-day%20%E2%80%98anushsthan%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20a%20government%20that%20is%20still%20officially%20secular%2C%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20state%20that%20%E2%80%9CGod%20(no%20less)%20has%20chosen%20me%20to%20represent%20the%20people%20of%20India%20during%20pran%20pratishta%E2%80%9D.%20Shortly%20thereafter%20came%20the%20endorsement%20from%20modern%20India%E2%80%99s%20Iron%20man-turned-yes-man%20who%20issued%20a%20public%20statement%20that%20Modi%20had%20been%20chosen%20by%20Lord%20Ram%20to%20preside%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20no%20mistake%3B%20we%20are%20beholding%20an%20extraordinary%20human%20phenomenon%20who%20has%20upended%20all%20the%20conventional%20norms%20of%20leadership.%20Self-awareness%2C%20humility%2C%20and%20respectfulness%20as%20personal%20traits%2C%20the%20assumption%20that%20the%20PM%20is%20only%20first%20among%20equals%2C%20collective%20decision-making%2C%20team%20spirit%2C%20and%20empowering%20delegation%20are%20attributes%20of%20leadership%20that%20Modi%20has%20contemptuously%20discarded.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20the%20entire%20polity%20%E2%80%93%20humans%20and%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20has%20slavishly%20revolved%20around%20this%20superman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20playing%20out%20before%20the%20country%20is%20an%20extreme%20form%20of%20deification.%20His%20devotees%20see%20him%20variously%20as%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20as%20an%20avatar%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Lord%20Krishna%2C%20as%20the%2011th%20avatar%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu.%20J.P.%20Nadda%20%E2%80%93%20sycophant%20supreme%20%E2%80%93%20went%20over%20the%20top%2C%20describing%20his%20master%20as%20the%20king%20of%20Gods.