mensional%2520measure%2520looks%2520at%2Cescaping%2520poverty%2520during%2520this%2520period.%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20claims%20a%20precipitate%20reduction%20in%20poverty%20levels.%20Through%20statistical%20sleight%20of%20hand%2C%20brilliantly%20described%20by%20one%20commentator%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmagical%20realism%E2%80%9D%2C%20multidimensional%20poverty%20is%20shown%20to%20have%20declined%20from%2029.1%25%20in%202013-14%20to%2011.28%25%20in%202022-23%2C%20thereby%20lifting%20about%2024.82%20crore%20people%20out%20of%20poverty.%20(What%20then%20does%20one%20make%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%20of%20providing%20foodgrains%20to%20more%20than%2080%20crore%20people%20free%20of%20cost%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%20%E2%80%93%20a%20case%20of%20carrying%20coal%20to%20Newcastle%3F)%20With%20the%20truth%20undermined%20and%20the%20distinction%20between%20fact%20and%20fantasy%20blurred%2C%20our%20Supreme%20Leader%20parades%20one%20falsehood%20after%20another%20with%20a%20disarming%20straight%20face!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20unabated%2C%20all-out%20government%20propaganda%20promoting%20our%20tinsel%20god%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20nothing%20more%20in-your-face%20in%20its%20unblushing%20projection%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Leader%20than%20the%20legislated%20diktat%20%E2%80%93%20flagrantly%20intended%20to%20stimulate%20cult%20worship%20%E2%80%93%20directing%20universities%20and%20Indian%20Railways%20to%20set%20up%20selfie%20points%20at%20select%20locations%20and%20stations%20with%20pictures%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20presumably%20to%20enable%20us%20to%20bask%20in%20reflected%20glory.%20There%20are%20official%20instructions%20to%20army%20men%20proceeding%20on%20leave%2C%20and%20sundry%20government%20officials%2C%20to%20tom-tom%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Modi%20sarkar.%20So%20universal%20is%20the%20plague%20that%20even%20our%20Covid%20vaccination%20certificates%20and%20the%205%20kg%20rice%20bags%20given%20as%20dole%20have%20our%20Supreme%20Leader%E2%80%99s%20trademark%20picture%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20the%20government%20but%20the%20BJP%20too%20has%20capitulated%20to%20the%20cult%20worship.%20Everybody%20else%20has%20been%20smudged%20out%2C%20including%20redoubtable%20stalwarts%20like%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi.%20Possible%20competitors%20of%20his%20alter%20ego%20such%20as%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20Shivraj%20Chauhan%2C%20and%20Vasundhara%20Raje%20Scindia%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20insignificance.%20By%20picking%20nonentities%20as%20chief%20ministers%20in%20the%20three%20States%20where%20the%20BJP%20recently%20won%20big%2C%20the%20clear%20message%20conveyed%20was%20that%20it%20is%20one%20man%20alone%20who%20wins%20elections%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Everyone%20else%20is%20dispensible!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20are%20witnessing%20today%20is%20no%20ordinary%20case%20of%20a%20leader%20in%20an%20exalted%20state%20of%20self-love%20or%20self-absorption%3B%20one%20suspects%20a%20deeper%20pathology%20that%20psychoanalysts%20have%20identified%20as%20narcissism.%20Equally%20unhinged%20is%20the%20ignoble%20servitude%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20devotees%20in%20the%20country%20who%20have%20come%20under%20the%20spell%20of%20this%20consummate%20artist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErich%20Fromm%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20psychoanalysts%20and%20social%20philosophers%2C%20who%20has%20delved%20deep%20into%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20narcissist%20and%20his%20symbiotic%20connection%20with%20his%20submissive%20%E2%80%9Cmasochistic%E2%80%9D%20devotee%2C%20helps%20us%20understand%20the%20bizarre%20idol%20worship%20in%20our%20country%20today.%20According%20to%20Fromm%2C%20man%E2%80%99s%20sanity%20depends%20on%20his%20relatedness%20and%20communion%20with%20other%20human%20beings.%20This%20transcending%20of%20lonely%20individual%20existence%20and%20unifying%20with%20the%20other%20humans%20is%20achieved%20by%20the%20narcissist%20through%20domination%20and%20by%20the%20bhakt%20through%20submission%20but%20in%20the%20process%20of%20feeding%20on%20each%20other%2C%20they%20both%20lose%20their%20integrity%20and%20freedom.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they%20lose%20the%20capacity%20for%20the%20one%20passion%20that%20inspires%20solidarity%20with%20our%20fellow%20creatures%20which%20is%20love%20and%20empathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20very%20abstruse%3F%20Put%20simply%2C%20the%20narcissist%20fails%20to%20develop%20the%20capacity%20for%20love%20because%20for%20him%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20only%20one%20reality%2C%20that%20of%20his%20own%20thought%20processes%2C%20feelings%20and%20needs%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Emotionally%20crippled%2C%20the%20narcissist%20sees%20the%20phenomena%20in%20the%20outside%20world%20only%20from%20the%20viewpoint%20of%20them%20being%20useful%20or%20dangerous%20to%20him.%20Fromm%20believes%20that%20in%20its%20most%20extreme%20form%2C%20narcissism%20can%20lead%20to%20insanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20submissive%20masochists%2C%20what%20is%20particularly%20disconcerting%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20overwhelming%20millions%20among%20us%20have%20enthusiastically%20bought%20into%20his%20overweening%20narcissism%20and%20sophistry.%20Which%20brings%20to%20mind%20Shakespeare%E2%80%99s%20brilliant%20diagnosis%20of%20why%20the%20egomaniacal%20Julius%20Caesar%20held%20sway%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%20doth%20bestride%20the%20narrow%20world%20like%20a%20Colossus%2C%20and%20we%20petty%20men%20walk%20under%20his%20huge%20legs%2C%20and%20peep%20about%20to%20find%20ourselves%20dishonourable%20graves%E2%80%A6.The%20fault%20dear%20Brutus%20is%20not%20in%20our%20stars%2C%20but%20in%20ourselves%2C%20that%20we%20are%20underlings%E2%80%A6.upon%20what%20meat%20(or%20dhokla)%20doth%20this%20our%20Caesar%20feed%20that%20he%20is%20grown%20so%20great%3F%E2%80%9D%20Shame%20on%20us!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705756813