dia%E2%80%99s%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Pakistan%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Ajay%20Bisaria%2C%20has%20accepted%20that%20we%20only%20have%20narratives%20but%20no%20proof%20of%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Balakot%20strike.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99ll%20perhaps%20never%20know%20for%20sure%E2%80%9D%20of%20how%20successful%20the%20strike%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2035-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bisaria%2C%20while%20discussing%20his%20views%2C%20said%20that%20the%20terrorists%20behind%20the%20Pulwama%20attack%20of%20February%202019%2C%20the%20fifth%20anniversary%20of%20which%20will%20fall%20next%20month%2C%20%E2%80%9Clucked%20out%20in%20getting%20an%20unprotected%20target%20in%20a%20convoy%20of%20vehicles%E2%80%9D%20and%20thus%20%E2%80%9Cmet%20with%20unexpected%20success%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBisaria%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20echoing%20what%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%2C%20who%20was%20the%20governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20at%20the%20time%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20year%2C%20when%20he%20claimed%20the%20terror%20attack%20was%20a%20result%20of%20%E2%80%9Cincompetence%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Elaparwahi%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20the%20Indian%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatya-pal-malik-full-interview-pulwama-modi%5C%22%3EPulwama%2C%20Modi%2C%20Corruption%3A%20Full%20Explosive%20Transcript%20of%20Satya%20Pal%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20Viral%20Interview%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20envoy%20was%20also%20asked%20what%20proof%20exists%20to%20corroborate%20the%20statement%20made%20by%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20of%20the%20time%2C%20which%20Bisaria%20quotes%20in%20his%20book.%20The%20statement%20is%20that%20at%20Balakot%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20very%20large%20number%20of%20JeM%20terrorists%2C%20trainers%2C%20senior%20commanders%2C%20and%