Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F21092005%2Fpablo-heimplatz-fVL0zZdk-R4-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20has%20issued%20guidelines%20to%20those%20facilitating%20religious%20conversions%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20during%20the%20process%20the%20facilitators%20must%20provide%20a%20detailed%20understanding%20of%20the%20religion%20that%20a%20person%20is%20converting%20to%2C%20its%20associated%20ramifications%2C%20and%20make%20the%20person%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20shifts%20in%20legal%20standing%2C%20post-conversion%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Finterfaith-marriage-delhi-hc-decrees-guidelines-for-changing-religion-101705687227561.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConversion%20to%20another%20religion%20which%20is%20uninformed%20may%20not%20prepare%20a%20convert%20with%20the%20consequences%20that%20they%20will%20now%20not%20be%20able%20to%20follow%20their%20form%20of%20religion%20in%20case%20the%20religion%20they%20are%20converting%20to%2C%20does%20not%20permit%20so.%20This%20becomes%20more%20critical%20in%20case%20their%20reverting%20back%20to%20their%20religion%20may%20ensue%20legal%2C%20matrimonial%2C%20succession%2C%20and%20custody-related%20consequences%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20the%20guidelines%20as%20part%20of%20a%20case%20it%20was%20hearing%20on%20Friday%2C%20January%2019%2C%20where%20a%20Muslim%20man%20petitioned%20the%20court%20to%20quash%20a%20rape%20complaint%20filed%20against%20him%20by%20a%20Hindu%20woman%20in%20October%202022.%20He%20was%20arrested%20on%20November%2018%2C%202022%20and%20was%20granted%20interim%20bail%20five%20days%20later%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20they%20had%20married%20according%20to%20Muslim%20customs%20and%20rights%20after%20the%20woman%20converted%20to%20Islam.%20He%20was%20granted%20regular%20in%20February%202023%20after%20the%20woman%20told%20the%20authorities%20that%20she%20married%20the%20man%2010%20days%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20registered%20against%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20then%20approached%20the%20court%20for%20the%20FIR%20against%20him%20to%20be%20quashed%20and%20told%20the%20court%20that%20he%20had%20settled%20his%20disputes%20with%20the%20woman%20and%20they%20were%20now%20legally%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20court%20declined%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR.%20Instead%2C%20the%20court%2C%20in%20a%2053-page%20verdict%2C%20issued%20guidelines%20to%20authorities%2Findividuals%20facilitating%20conversion%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20inform%20the%20individual%20with%20exhaustive%20information%20concerning%20the%20religious%20doctrines%2C%20customs%2C%20and%20practices%20associated%20with%20the%20chosen%20faith%20in%20a%20native%20language%20to%20ensure%20that%20consent%20to%20such%20conversion%20is%20an%20informed%20consent%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEqually%20important%20is%20the%20exploration%20of%20religious%20repercussions.%20The%20individual%20must%20be%20apprised%20of%20the%20religious%20norms%2C%20obligations%2C%20and%20restrictions%20that%20come%20with%20the%20conversion%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20told%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20obtain%20an%20affidavit%20from%20the%20parties%20wishing%20to%20convert%20indicating%20their%20age%2C%20marital%20history%2C%20and%20marital%20status%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20interfaith%20marriage.%20It%20also%20said%20affidavits%20must%20be%20obtained%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20the%20conversion%20is%20voluntary%20after%20understanding%20the%20implications%20related%20to%20marital%20divorce%2C%20succession%2C%20custody%2C%20and%20religious%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20Justice%20Sharma%20said%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20illiterate%20and%20did%20not%20know%20Urdu%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ENikahnama%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20showed%20that%20the%20contents%20of%20either%20the%20marriage%20or%20conversion%20certificate%20which%20were%20also%20in%20Urdu%20were%20explained%20to%20her.%20She%20refused%20to%20quash%20the%20FIR%20against%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705737948000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F21092005%2Fpablo-heimplatz-fVL0zZdk-R4-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-issues-guidelines-for-couples-converting-religion-for-the-sake-of-marriages%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Swarana%20Kanta%20Sharma%20said%20the%20facilitators%20must%20provide%20a%20detailed%20understanding%20of%20the%20religion%20that%20a%20person%20is%20converting%20to%2C%20its%20associated%20ramifications%2C%20and%20make%20the%20person%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20shifts%20in%20legal%20standing%2C%20post-conversion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-issues-guidelines-for-couples-converting-religion-for-the-sake-of-marriages%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Mothers%20Killed%20Each%20Hour%20in%20Gaza%20Conflict%3A%20UN%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06132249%2FCooking-in-war.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unwomen.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-01%2FGender%2520Alert%2520The%2520Gendered%2520Impact%2520of%2520the%2520Crisis%2520in%2520Gaza.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ereport%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20examines%20the%20gendered%20impact%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20which%20has%20left%20more%20than%2023%2C000%20Palestinians%20dead%2C%20according%20to%20Gazan%20health%20authorities%2C%20about%2016%2C000%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20or%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFailure%20and%20trauma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20evidenced%20once%20more%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20the%20first%20victims%20of%20conflict%20and%20that%20our%20duty%20to%20seek%20peace%20is%20a%20duty%20to%20them.%20We%20are%20failing%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unwomen.org%2Fen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUN%20Women%3C%2Fa%3E%20Executive%20Director%20Sima%20Bahous%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unwomen.org%2Fen%2Fnews-stories%2Fstatement%2F2024%2F01%2Fstatement-on-gaza-by-un-women-executive-director-sima-bahous%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20alongside%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20failure%2C%20and%20the%20generational%20trauma%20inflicted%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20over%20these%20100%20days%20and%20counting%2C%20will%20haunt%20all%20of%20us%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20of%207th%20October%20and%20the%20horrors%20that%20have%20followed%2C%20especially%20in%20Gaza%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20evidenced%20once%20more%20that%20women%20and%20children%20are%20the%20first%20victims%20of%20conflict.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatement%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Funwomenchief%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40unwomenchief%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sima%20Bahous%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRWf2vhOI7E%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRWf2vhOI7E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5a9jgKFvyK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5a9jgKFvyK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20UN%20Women%20(%40UN_Women)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_Women%2Fstatus%2F1748360205698515306%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Women%20also%20reiterated%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20accounts%20of%20unconscionable%20sexual%20violence%20and%20other%20gender-based%20violence%20during%20the%20Hamas-led%20attacks%20against%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20that%20sparked%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20called%20for%20accountability%2C%20justice%20and%20support%20for%20all%20those%20affected%20and%20for%20the%20immediate%20and%20unconditional%20release%20of%20all%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Impossible%20decisions%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Women%20said%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20%E2%80%9Cis%20fundamentally%20a%20protection%20crisis%20for%20women%E2%80%9D%20at%20a%20time%20when%20nowhere%20in%20the%20enclave%20is%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%201.9%20million%20people%20now%20displaced%2C%20close%20to%20a%20million%20are%20women%20and%20girls%2C%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible%20decisions%E2%80%9D%20they%20have%20to%20make%20regarding%20whether%20to%20evacuate%20%E2%80%93%20when%20and%20how%20as%20well%20as%20where%20to%20go%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Care%20entrenched%20with%20gender%20differentiated%20fears%20and%20experiences%E2%80%9D%2C%20given%20risks%20of%20attacks%20and%20harassment%20while%20on%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20Women%20further%20estimated%20that%20at%20least%203%2C000%20women%20may%20have%20become%20widows%20and%20heads%20of%20households%2C%20and%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20children%20may%20now%20be%20fatherless.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20more%20women%20fear%20families%20will%20resort%20to%20desperate%20coping%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20early%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20organisations%20continue%20to%20operate%20amidst%20the%20crisis.%20In%20November%2C%20UN%20Women%20conducted%20a%20rapid%20survey%20of%2012%20women-led%20organisations%20and%20one%20youth-led%20group%20which%20found%20that%20most%20%E2%80%93%2083%25%20%E2%80%93%20were%20at%20least%20partially%20operating%2C%20focused%20mainly%20on%20the%20emergency%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20less%20than%201%25%20of%20funding%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fflash-appeal-2023-glance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20Flash%20Appeal%20for%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20directly%20gone%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20the%20course%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20part%20of%20UN%20Women%E2%80%99s%20six-month%20response%20plan%20for%20Gaza%2C%20which%20includes%20providing%20emergency%20food%20assistance%20to%20over%2014%2C000%20female-headed%20households%20and%20supporting%20the%20distribution%20of%20items%20requested%20by%20women%20on%20the%20ground%20such%20as%20clothing%2C%20sanitary%20products%20and%20baby%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20is%20also%20partnering%20with%20women-led%20organizations%20to%20deliver%20gender%20responsive%20services%20for%20gender-based%20violence%2C%20establishing%20women-led%20protection%20and%20response%20committees%20in%20shelters%20and%20convening%20regular%20consultations%20with%20women%E2%80%99s%20organizations%20to%20discuss%20the%20challenges%20they%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F01%2F1145707%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fe