%3EThe%20rediscovery%20of%20his%20art%20began%20in%201906%20with%20a%20small%20exhibition%20in%20Berlin%20that%20presented%20paintings%20and%20sculptures%20from%20the%20period%20of%201775%20to%201875%2C%20and%20included%2032%20works%20by%C2%A0Friedrich.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20launched%20a%20phase%20of%20popularity%20that%20continues%20to%20this%20day.%20Friedrich%20never%20signed%20any%20of%20his%20paintings%20because%20he%20believed%20his%20name%20would%20never%20be%20forgotten.%20So%20far%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fgermany-celebrates-250-years-of-caspar-david-friedrich%2Fa-67595101%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705733178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20120618%2Fimage-1769.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fgermany-celebrates-250-years-of-caspar-david-friedrich%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Romantic%20painter%20Caspar%20David%20Friedrich%20is%20one%20of%20Germany's%20most%20famous%20painters.%20As%20the%20250th%20anniversary%20year%20of%20his%20birth%20starts%2C%20DW%20takes%20a%20look%20at%20his%20life%20and%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fgermany-celebrates-250-years-of-caspar-david-friedrich%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20bogies%20of%20Kannur-Alappuzha%20Executive%20Express%20derail%2C%20train%20delayed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705732558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F01%2Ffull%2F1682943815-5767.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Ftwo-bogies-of-kannur-alappuzha-executive-express-derail-train-delayed-124012000143_