pdates-on-jan-20-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-reliance-hul-124012000057_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-on-jan-20-sensex-nifty-gift-nifty-reliance-hul-124012000057_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Need%20to%20Study%20if%20Any%20%E2%80%98Enemy'%20Involved%20in%20Rise%20of%20Natural%20Disasters%20in%20Border%20Areas%3A%20Rajnath%20Singh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F20113634%2Fimage-1762.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20on%20Friday%20(January%2019)%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20increasing%20number%20of%20natural%20disasters%20in%20certain%20border%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%2C%20suggesting%20a%20need%20for%20a%20detailed%20study%20to%20determine%20if%20any%20%E2%80%98enemy%20country%E2%80%99%20is%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCertain%20border%20States%20like%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20Union%20Territories%20like%20Ladakh%20have%20noticed%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20natural%20disasters%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20Himalayas%20extend%20to%20other%20states%20as%20well%2C%20but%20such%20incidents%20are%20confined%20to%20certain%20states%20only%2C%20and%20we%20cannot%20ignore%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20climate%20change%20is%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20weather-related%20phenomenon%20but%20is%20also%20linked%20to%20national%20security%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Frajnath-singh-natural-disasters-joshimath-crisis-9118129%2F%5C%22%3Enews%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Frajnath-hints-at-the-enemy-country-behind-extreme-natural-disasters-in-border-states%2Farticle67756649.ece%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20experts%20believe%20that%20these%20natural%20disasters%20are%20an%20outcome%20of%20climate%20change.%20Climate%20change%20in%20the%20country%20is%20not%20just%20a%20weather-related%20phenomenon%3B%20the%20matter%20is%20related%20to%20national%20security.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20(MoD)%20has%20taken%20it%20very%20seriously%20and%20will%20seek%20help%20from%20friendly%20countries%20to%20study%20and%20rule%20out%20any%20involvement%20of%20any%20enemy%20country%20on%20this%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%C2%A0%20minister%20made%20these%20comments%20during%20an%20event%20at%20Joshimath-Malari%20Road%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20where%20he%20inaugurated%2035%20infrastructure%20projects%20of%20the%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2035%20projects%20include%2029%20bridges%20and%20six%20roads.%20The%20border%20infrastructure%20projects%20will%20boost%20connectivity%20to%20the%20LAC%20and%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%2C%20thus%20facilitating%20swift%20military%20movement%20to%20the%20borders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Frajnath-singh-natural-disasters-joshimath-crisis-9118129%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20came%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20China%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-is-continuing-to-build-infrastructure-along-lac-border-with-bhutan-pentagon%5C%22%3Eramping%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20border%20infrastructure%20along%20the%20nearly%203%2C500%20kilometre-long%20LAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajnath%20Singh%20emphasised%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%C2%A0%20views%20border%20areas%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20mainstream%2C%20not%20merely%20a%20buffer%20zone.%20He%20highlighted%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20develop%20mountainous%20infrastructure%20and%20strategically%20position%20troops%20on%20hill%20borders%2C%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20residents%20and%20enhancing%20military%20capabilities%20against%20adversaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20concern%20over%20significant%20migration%20from%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20border%20areas%2C%20the%20defence%20minister%20noted%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20extending%20infrastructure%20development%20schemes%20to%20every%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underscored%20the%20vital%20role%20of%20border%20residents%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20living%20near%20the%20borders%20are%20no%20less%20than%20soldiers.%20If%20a%20soldier%20protects%20the%20country%20by%20wearing%20a%20uniform%2C%20the%20residents%20of%20border%20areas%20are%20serving%20the%20motherland%20in%20their%20own%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20organised%20on%20the%20Dhak%20Bridge%2C%20a%2093-metre-long%20Class%2070R%20bridge%20over%20Dhak%20Nallah%20that%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20Singh%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Dhak%20Bridge%20assumes%20strategic%20importance%20as%20it%20will%20provide%20increased%20connectivity%20to%20the%20borders%20and%20enhance%20operational%20preparedness%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20defence%20ministry%20statement%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%20It%20added%20that%20it%20will%20also%20boost%20the%20socio-economic%20development%20of%20the%20region%20as%20it%20is%20the%20only%20road%20connecting%20villages%20from%20Joshimath%20to%20Niti%20Pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20not%20only%20promote%20tourism%2C%20but%20also%20generate%20more%20employment%20opportunities%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%2034%20projects%20include%2038.25-km%20long%20Ragini-Ustad-Pharkian%20Gali%20Road%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20which%20will%20provide%20all%20weather%20connectivity%20between%20the%20Valley%E2%80%99s%20Tangdhar%20and%20Keran%20sectors%2C%20the%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%2